They don’t have CAD released but you can look at their build blog

Beşiktaş Rsports 9483 | 2023 Off-season Build Blog Technical Discussion
Well, welcome to our blog, I guess. This thread will be about our off-season journey and our new robot which has been in the making. Creating a blog has been a last minute decision, so we have come a little way. Before we get technical, let’s start by discussing our goals and situations. We have many new members to the crew!!! Our first priority is getting them engaged with the rest of the team. The “???” in the title is about us not having an official team number after some unpleasant inciden…

I believe that their rack an pinion intake is based off of 254’s 2023 robot, who also doesn’t have public CAD.
254 did a writeup on it, it’s a 10DP profile cut into a polycarb sheet with a 10DP pinion on a falcon driving it if I remember correctly.
